edu.harvard.integer.service.technology

Interface TechnologyManagerInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BaseManagerInterface
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    TechnologyManagerLocalInterface, TechnologyManagerRemoteInterface
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TechnologyManager

    public interface TechnologyManagerInterface
extends BaseManagerInterface
    The TechnologyManagerInterface is the API to the business service technology hierarchy. This interface has all methods to add/delete/modify/query the objects in the technology hierarchy from the business service down the the mechanism. The Capabilities are accessed via the ManagementObjectCapablityManager.
